title: Sound of the 70's : Get it On

sources.title: Sound of the 70's : Get it On
sources.description:
Since The Buggles ushered in the end of the radio star and the birth of video-pop, music has never been the same. This episode of Sounds of the 1970s chronicles an era where teen idols shared the spotlight with punk rebels. Witness the glam-rock theatrics of Sweet and T. Rex, the soulful genius of Bill Withers, the raw energy of The Damned, and unforgettable performances by The Boomtown Rats, Bay City Rollers, Squeeze, The Stranglers, The Hollies, Focus, Dr. Hook, Mink DeVille, and 10cc. With archival news footage and iconic performances, relive the moment when bubblegum pop collided with punk rebellion to make musical history

Some amazing times and some unforgettable performances..

Director: Jason Fenwick
Year 2021
